    Populates the global enviroment with cluster groupings based on t-SNE data

    MakeClusterList.Rd

    This function groups t-SNE data points into clusters using a specified threshold and visualizes the clusters.

    MakeClusterList(ptmtable, toolong = 3.5)

    Arguments

    ptmtable

    A dataset for post-translational modifications.

    toolong

    A numeric threshold for cluster separation, defaults to 3.5.

    Examples

    MakeClusterList(ptmtable, toolong =  3.5)
